Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.70,0:00:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.77,0:00:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上的時候 傷囗就像假的一樣不痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這都無所謂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.02,0:00:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛都無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.86,0:00:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這股在體內沸騰的衝動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.37,0:00:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體中有什麼狂暴的東西湧現出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.08,0:00:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 身 體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 的這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.04,0:00:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 血 肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻上一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.59,0:00:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.21,0:00:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 骨 髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻上你的一切吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,獻 上 生 命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.72,0:00:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑的形狀在...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.24,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.70,0:02:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你的真正實力嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.41,0:02:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣才有粉碎的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.88,0:02:43.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的龐大身體打飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.97,0:02:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等的蠻力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是剛才那個男人的攻擊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.98,0:03:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然弄碎了我這連炮彈都能擋住的盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個手舞大劍身穿甲冑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是人類可以做出的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.54,0:03:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙義肢上裝著大炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.71,0:03:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直就像怪物一樣弓雖悍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.59,0:03:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天感覺不太一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.51,0:03:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻假手是大炮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.39,0:03:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.77,0:03:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有危險 如果繼續那樣的戰鬥下去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從剛才開始你是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.23,0:03:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的凱茲先生傷囗並未合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.98,0:03:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是感覺不到囗的疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是礦精製作成的咒物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.08,0:03:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂戰士的甲冑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂戰士的 甲冑?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.87,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上那副甲冑後 再與寄宿其中的不祥之氣同步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.17,0:04:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會如同鬼神一般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.80,0:04:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被強烈的感情控制 忘記痛苦和恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類為了不讓自己的肉體受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.93,0:04:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會無意識地設定力量的上限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.48,0:04:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼痛 是防止自己的肉體受傷的警報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.19,0:04:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去痛感的人 會發揮出不得了的力量和速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後超出人體的極限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.40,0:04:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入生命的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.87,0:04:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 格斯他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.54,0:04:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 氣的活動太劇烈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我的念話無法傳達過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等的宿敵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.76,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼以我這會心一擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什縻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.99,0:05:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遒次單挑是你勝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.58,0:05:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來傳言不假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.25,0:05:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你是遠超其上的超級戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.34,0:05:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 從現在開始我的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃是為了吾主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.01,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作光之鷹的使徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當你的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.61,0:05:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用使徒被授予的力量 埋葬黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面打中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.37,0:05:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能 竟然擋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.25,0:06:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類把使徒的攻擊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不承認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.51,0:06:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比鋼鐵還堅硬的我的鋼王的皮膚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.89,0:06:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龜裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.10,0:06:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.40,0:06:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 剛才手腳轉向相反的方向了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.66,0:06:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是甲冑的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.70,0:06:42.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲冑在補給折斷的手腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貫穿血肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.54,0:06:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餵食骨髓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.33,0:06:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說以前那副甲冑的持有者就像那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.21,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個身體被甲冑的鐵齒蠶食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.55,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到全身的骨頭碎裂 全身的血液噴干還仍然戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.93,0:06:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後斷氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼把那麼危險的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給瀕死的凱茲穿上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.39,0:07:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為了讓同伴活下去 總要有犧栍嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.52,0:07:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 因為我的錯 又要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.19,0:07:16.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人 為什麼 為什把那種東西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.41,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.41,0:07:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是只有你這個魔法師才能做到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我還不成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內心又混亂 魔術會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.30,0:07:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚自身的稚嫩 知曉沉溺於力量的危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此 現在的你才能夠做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那身處力量的亂流中的劍士先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要向他展現道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.36,0:07:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 做怎麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去把凱茲先生帶回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.19,0:07:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體就拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試試看吧 師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託是 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.33,0:08:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.83,0:08:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然第二次擋住了我這樣形態發出的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.84,0:08:13.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還讓我受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍大哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們也加入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.14,0:08:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找魔女的人太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也不能間著不做事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像你也很棘手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.02,0:08:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.10,0:08:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.77,0:08:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對使徒來說 單挑根本就無所謂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.11,0:08:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在變身的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.54,0:08:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個觸感 有四五根肋骨斷了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.26,0:08:59.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥方式漸漸不像人類了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.55,0:09:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.43,0:09:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 那簡直就像...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.27,0:09:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊有好像很好吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.52,0:09:13.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一有什麼不測
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.81,0:09:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就抱上希凱兒逃走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.86,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.94,0:09:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.87,0:09:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是寄生在甲冑上的憎惡的亂流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得及嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被這種東西吞食的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人的自我會支離破碎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.72,0:09:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生的憎惡 增幅甲冑的氣但不是憎惡的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生就在這裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.36,0:09:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能辦到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.73,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這麼巨大的亂流中把人救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是失手我也會被這亂流吞沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.16,0:10:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是猶豫的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光之泡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.22,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生記憶的片段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像燈火一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.73,0:10:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成群的暗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.40,0:10:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 什麼啊 好可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.86,0:10:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捲進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.50,0:10:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.80,0:11:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.02,0:11:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 這是凱茲先生的自我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.19,0:11:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人的護符防止了自我的崩潿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 不能隨波逐流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨波
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 你會因為你而消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.37,0:11:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會被這領域拉進去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.29,0:11:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.13,0:11:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I KΣ?Λ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,HБАЯьыъц
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.30,0:11:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使徒 敵人 朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.76,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古力菲斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.43,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.68,0:11:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能怎樣都可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.90,0:12:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你旅行的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了怎樣都可以的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.03,0:12:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的靈魂是不會如此破爛不堪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.07,0:12:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.12,0:12:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.34,0:12:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.68,0:12:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.14,0:12:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.65,0:12:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不要碰她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.27,0:12:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回憶起來她的名字是喀絲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.94,0:12:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喀絲 卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.53,0:12:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字是 凱茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是烙印的劍士 凱茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.29,0:13:00.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是保護烙印的女子喀絲卡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.84,0:13:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承受我的灼熱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.77,0:13:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 喀絲卡小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.05,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.35,0:14:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.56,0:14:04.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.19,0:14:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.03,0:14:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.04,0:14:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且好年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.04,0:14:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得不錯 希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.17,0:14:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這片森林也撐不了多久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.84,0:14:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈樹燒毀的話這岸領域也就會關閉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.43,0:14:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣 我不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.85,0:14:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是古老東西飄蕩的時間的峽谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和這棵樹的壽命也太長了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算陽光再如何舒適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.24,0:15:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的東西也不能水遠停留在身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.96,0:15:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離巢的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.83,0:15:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開這裡 找到自己的道路吧 我得意的弟子喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.92,0:15:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你相處的時間雖然短暫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.51,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻是我一生中最為安逸的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.85,0:15:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.14,0:15:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.60,0:15:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.02,0:15:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.52,0:15:32.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 黑色劍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.94,0:15:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼火焰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.20,0:15:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為火龍的我也無法控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.49,0:15:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命只是變了形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在你夢中再見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.21,0:15:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否抓住眼前的命運就靠你自己了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.21,0:15:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福你的成長 我親愛的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.18,0:16:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永別了 我的陽光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.12,0:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.25,0:16:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是抵抗組織的人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.88,0:16:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.59,0:16:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是米特蘭軍阿古羅騎士團團長拉班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.39,0:16:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 拉班大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.81,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,團長竟然親自前來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.90,0:16:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,們至今的所作所為 作為武人深感敬佩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.32,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 抵抗組織只是空有其名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.49,0:17:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在暗地裡倉皇逃命已經很吃力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在溫達姆城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很難想像還是現世 已經化為魔都了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗者全部處死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.26,0:17:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓住的人 不論身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都當成戰奴送上戰場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人們被關在城堡裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.64,0:17:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被用於庫夏人的奇怪儀式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.02,0:17:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生死不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.07,0:17:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只乘|下老弱病殘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何等可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.87,0:17:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還有一線希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.87,0:17:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎爾露特公主還健在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.71,0:17:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聰說被關在那個再生之塔的頂層了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.79,0:17:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此話當真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千真萬確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.05,0:18:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了得到這條情報 我們失去了很多的同胞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人沒事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.89,0:18:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皇家的血脈沒有斷就有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.02,0:18:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉班大人 我們被困在都城不知道外界的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想確認一個聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.91,0:18:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鷹 在何處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.08,0:18:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙 是他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.79,0:18:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉班大人 這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.13,0:18:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個怪物究竟是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏人的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.30,0:18:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,庫夏人用魔法控制那些半人半獸的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.98,0:18:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說剛親眼得見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時城市被大霧籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.99,0:19:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像被霧召喚而來 怪物們開始在街上橫行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.79,0:19:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市民們深感恐懼 都躲在屋裡不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.39,0:19:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箭? 從哪裡來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.49,0:19:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫達姆的市民們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.09,0:20:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在暫且躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.80,0:20:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天捲走城中瘴氣的強風會吹起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.98,0:20:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還身負任務 就此告辭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.11,0:20:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躲藏忍耐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.11,0:20:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到鷹帶來風暴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.05,0:22:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好高興啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.05,0:22:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小孩啊 不過就是一個大水坑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.85,0:22:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 希凱兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.57,0:22:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.58,0:22:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凱茲先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.88,0:22:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身體可沒有那麼纖弱 不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.05,0:22:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還是把那身甲冑脫下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起碼靜養四五天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.72,0:23:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來我就差不多睡了一個月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.64,0:23:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再磨蹭下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖說不想戰鬥的時候那樣完全感不到疼痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是多虧它旅行才能繼續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.32,0:23:15.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是被詛咒的鎧甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.91,0:23:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再戰鬥的話不知何時又會失控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.70,0:23:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那時候 不是還有一個可靠的魔法師嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.33,0:23:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都是精靈 現在就一起黏黏糊糊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.71,0:23:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是再發生那種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.51,0:23:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算現在不能保證性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.13,0:23:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.68,0:23:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為再也見不到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.44,0:23:51.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在陽光下 如此的閒逸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.80,0:24:05.59,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}…精靈 地獄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.10,0:24:10.18,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}能教我魔法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.31,0:24:14.48,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}我在回不了頭的旅行裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.56,0:24:18.65,Preview,,0,0,0,,起霧了 有什麼要來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.69,0:24:22.65,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an7}這副遲鈍的身體 變得破破爛爛正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.08,0:00:58.58,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\blur3.5\pos(1000,770)}火焰的啟程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.07,0:24:28.16,Title,,0,0,0,,{\b0\bord0\shad0\pos(970,800)\fs95}被告知的預兆
